metadata.description:
Lizard Impression is a collection of 10,000 unique AI NFTs, created by Meteor Labs, a platform where everyone becomes an artist.

We are a Web 3.0 AI-based platform that helps users automatically generate creative images and short videos from text, images or videos. The PFP holders are website VIP members. They own the PFP copyright, get more token airdrops and yields on site use, and have exclusive entry to membership areas and perks. They access most of the site functions for free - all art styles in particular. Company clients benefit from our SaaS based institutional service as well.

Our natural token serves as payment for site purchases, accessibility and circulation. Users earn token rewards in accord with their site activities and community contribution. It is the governance rights in MeteorDAO.

We endeavor to become the largest AI artist community and metaverse along roadmap activation. See meteorlabs.org for more details.
